&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1447#issuecomment-163555582&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1447#issuecomment-163555582&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    +1 for the Kafka part.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15052989" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 11 Dec 2015 16:37:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user asfgit closed the pull request at:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1447&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1447&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15053026" author="aljoscha" created="Fri, 11 Dec 2015 17:05:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/6bd5714d2a045e581b1a761830d010598f803de7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/commit/6bd5714d2a045e581b1a761830d010598f803de7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15054424" author="rmetzger" created="Sat, 12 Dec 2015 17:10:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just for clarification: Your fix resolves the issue for Kafka sources, but other sources might still suffer from it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15055817" author="aljoscha" created="Mon, 14 Dec 2015 10:50:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Correct, but I think other sources don&apos;t behave like Kafka does, in that it knows that it will never receive data but still stays in an infinite loop without finishing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
